      "rationale": "Solver residual convergence plots are not provided in the submission package. Floating-point sensitivity analysis was not performed. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5; achieved level defaulted to 1."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Use error",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "User influence study performed varying mesh topology decisions, turbulence model constants, and boundary condition interpretation; sensitivity bounds reported.",
      "rationale": "No user influence study was conducted. The impact of analyst choices on hemolysis index predictions is unknown. Flagged as epistemic gap."
    },
    {
