      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 5,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Alternative hemolysis model forms (Giersiepen-Wurzinger, Bludszuweit) compared; model form uncertainty quantified and bounded relative to clinical threshold.",
      "rationale": "Only the power-law Giersiepen-Wurzinger model was used. No comparison against alternative model forms was performed. Model form uncertainty is unquantified. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
